Well, it's relevant (to me at least) because I am curious to know the opinions of a wider audience than my particular circle. I meant no offense by asking that particular question and I hope none was taken and that you are not overly frustrated with my question. <br>
<br>
To me, the clickable effect is the only reason to get it. Perhaps for some the epic is primarily a status symbol and they never actually use it. For others doing their epic is not even under consideration and they're doing just fine without it.<br>
<br>
<br>
